    {
      "provider_name": "Removery (Bucktown)",
      "location_city": "Chicago",
      "location_state": "IL",
      "method_used": "PicoWay",
      "review_text": "I started removal for two of my tats at Removery about 2 years ago. I had already been in the removal process for about a year prior somewhere else. The laser Removery uses is SIGNIFICANTLY less painful than what I experienced at the place I was going before, which claimed to have had “the newest technology” (obviously bs). Removal is of course never going to be comfortable, but I would say the pain level with Removery’s laser is about a 4/10 compared to dang near close to a 10/10 at the other place.\nI had some issues regarding a misleading consultation that resulted in unfair pricing, however, Angie the studio manager eagerly stepped in to help with a quick & fair solution. She is super sweet, along with all of the staff I’ve met at this location!\nI’m still in the long & dreadful removal process unfortunately, but Removery is trying to get the job done as quickly as possible while also ensuring not to cause any additional skin damage I obtained at my prior removal place. I’m almost at the finish line, but super happy Removery prioritizes quality treatment over speed!",
      "star_rating": 5,
